# 🧠🚀 NexaKing (NXK) Roadmap

## 🌌 Our Vision for the Future
**NexaKing (NXK)** is built to lead a new wave of decentralized innovation — long-term focused, transparent, and centered around AI & Ethereum synergy. No VCs. No hype. Just verifiable progress.

---

## 🪐 Phase 1: Foundation & Launch (Year 1)

### ✅ Token Launch & Uniswap Listing
- Deploy $NXK as an ERC-20 token on Ethereum mainnet
- Pair 2.5 ETH with NXK for initial liquidity
- Lock LP on Uniswap for long-term community trust

### 🧠 Website, SEO & AI-Focused Content
- Launch **NexaKing.com** with full branding suite
- Schedule and auto-publish 300 blog posts over 5 years
- Focus content on AI governance, smart cities, and crypto ecosystems

### 🌍 Community & Platform Visibility
- Register **NXK** on ENS: `enx.eth`
- Announce token on platforms like **DexTools**, **DexScreener**, and **CoinGecko**
- Set up social auto-posting to:
  - 🐦 X (Twitter)  
  - 💬 Telegram (dedicated)  
  - 🦣 Mastodon,  
  - 💻 LinkedIn  
  - 📌 Pinterest  
  - 📢 Discord, Quora, Substack, Medium

### 🔐 Smart Contract Security
- Public verification of contract renouncement or timelock
- Add contract address and CA hash to GitHub and NexaKing.com

---

## 🔭 Phase 2: Expansion & Reputation (Year 2)

### 📊 Cross-Chain Development
- Explore NXK bridging to BSC, Solana, and zkSync
- Begin listing process on secondary DEXs (Raydium, PancakeSwap)

### 🤝 Partnerships & Collaborations
- Reach out to other AI-focused or Ethereum-aligned communities
- Join or initiate DAOs for AI x DeFi experimentation

### 🎯 Growth Campaigns
- Run Learn-to-Earn educational campaigns with NXK rewards
- Host themed challenges around AI writing, creativity, and smart contracts

---

## 🔮 Phase 3: Ecosystem Scaling & Use-Cases (Year 3+)

### 🏛️ Decentralized Governance
- Launch Community Treasury DAO (5% of supply)
- Allow voting on blog themes, token use, and treasury spending

### 💡 Innovation Hubs
- Launch mini-grants for AI-ETH experiments
- Partner with indie developers to integrate NXK utility in tools

### 📈 Community-Driven Apps
- Release tools like:
  - AI-powered token watchlist
  - Smart contract verifier for public users
  - On-chain proposal & feedback tools for NXK holders

---

> ⚙️ Stay updated on the journey at **[NexaKing.com](https://nexaking.com)** or follow the rooster everywhere @W3Rooster!
